cs.LO, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.FL, cs.DS 

The paper proposes a new specification theory for component-based software systems that captures quantitative aspects during the refinement and implementation process. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Software Engineering (cs.SE), Programming Languages (cs.PL), Formal Languages and Automata Theory (cs.FL), and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) sub-categories.
